{"tid":620014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，依家支那比美國經濟制裁，更加要同佢劃清界線","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T02:28:36.000Z","uid":73915,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"204c784f4863ebda864e21d525bbe74750c13a97","tid":620014,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"乜撚野貿易戰<br />\n開頭聽都覺的怪怪地<br />\n諗真其實係比美國單方面制裁<br />\n係支那奶共傳媒先打飛機咩貿易戰<br />\n戰？邊撚度戰？呢d一向係叫經濟制裁<br />\n<br />\n今晚戴耀廷，有咩要正式啟動就啟動埋佢<br />\n要港獨就一次過爭取無謂拖拖拉拉，閃閃縮縮<br />\n反正依家香港全方面一舊屎<br />\n政府全面犧牲香港佢奶共<br />\n燒埋完本唔受影響既中產，基層<br />\n氣數應該差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd11e470738f21df53b833078b4c10df933e68ca","tid":620014,"uid":40628,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is not China"},{"pid":"5cb064b1889869c0ba790e53b4999b0e4a681514","tid":620014,"uid":24140,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"明既人一早明<br />\n<br />\n一般曬人最少要等到無野食，無工開先會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e54154a4c45cb3aa6237c4c4f15888802089e62","tid":620014,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5cb064b1889869c0ba790e53b4999b0e4a681514","tid":620014,"uid":24140,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"明既人一早明<br />\n<br />\n一般曬人最少要等到無野食，無工開先會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"即係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84db6f17b8cd6e200b64c9809eb15c2397df79b4","tid":620014,"uid":24140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0e54154a4c45cb3aa6237c4c4f15888802089e62","tid":620014,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5cb064b1889869c0ba790e53b4999b0e4a681514","tid":620014,"uid":24140,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy"